{"tid":1452924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廢除香港法例第232章 《警隊條例》","createTime":"2019-08-12T02:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:59:25.000Z","uid":92170,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d5e452cd9cad91832c8b0f3adfcd5fe81a7a0de2","tid":1452924,"uid":92170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:47:04.000Z","msg":"自2019年6月9日起，特別是721及822警隊之行動及結果，有大量證據及事件，足夠以香港警務處違反第香港法例第383章 《香港人權法案條例》，包括第五條《人身自由和安全》、第十一條《被控告或判定犯有刑事罪的人的權利》、第十四條《對私生活、家庭、住宅、通信、名譽及信用的保護》、第十六條《意見和發表的自由》、第十七條《和平集會的權利》、第二十條《兒童的權利》及第二十二條《在法律前平等及受法律平等保護》等，應直接向法院申請司法覆核，廢除香港法例第232章 《警隊條例》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3cefdfc2bdc380b9d9ae03da983e21a1071192b","tid":1452924,"uid":92170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:50:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf4e343a0d8acf03db1e039474cec00c160102b","tid":1452924,"uid":75543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3cefdfc2bdc380b9d9ae03da983e21a1071192b","tid":1452924,"uid":92170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:50:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:52:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67e813faf7977eddb5e2efcfd94ecb2d7842fc13","tid":1452924,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:55:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pi